```plantuml
@startuml lowtalkers_escape-reality

actor User
participant "React Client" as Client
participant "Node.js Server" as Server
participant "AWS S3" as S3
participant "MariaDB" as DB
participant "Wikipedia API" as Wiki

User -> Client: Uploads 360° image
Client -> Server: POST /api/upload (image data)
Server -> S3: Upload image file
S3 --> Server: Return image URL
Server -> DB: Store image metadata (url, user_id)
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Return success + image URL

User -> Client: Selects VR scene
Client -> Server: GET /api/scenes
Server -> DB: Query scene data
DB --> Server: Return scene list
Server --> Client: Return scene data
Client -> Client: Render VR scene (A-Frame)

User -> Client: Adds comment (voice/text)
Client -> Server: POST /api/comments (text/audio)
Server -> DB: Store comment
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Return success

User -> Client: Likes a photo
Client -> Server: POST /api/likes (photo_id)
Server -> DB: Update like count
DB --> Server: Confirm update
Server --> Client: Return updated count

User -> Client: Searches Wikipedia
Client -> Server: GET /api/wiki?query=...
Server -> Wiki: Fetch Wikipedia articles
Wiki --> Server: Return article data
Server --> Client: Return formatted results

User -> Client: Bookmarks article
Client -> Server: POST /api/bookmarks (article_data)
Server -> DB: Store bookmark
DB --> Server: Confirm storage
Server --> Client: Return success

@enduml
```